msgid "na taṃ anugaṃ bhavissatī’ti. "
msgstr "It will not follow me to my next life.’ "

msgctxt "an10.219:11.7"
msgid "Evaṃ bhāvitā kho, bhikkhave, upekkhā cetovimutti anāgāmitāya saṃvattati, idha paññassa bhikkhuno uttari vimuttiṃ appaṭivijjhato”ti. "
